msgstr "Ou como um plug-in do Claude Code:"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-07-introducing-agent-mcp.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The README covers configuration for VS Code, Cursor, Windsurf, JetBrains, and other MCP-compatible tools."
msgstr "O README abrange a configuração do VS Code, Cursor, Windsurf, JetBrains e outras ferramentas compatíveis com o MCP."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-07-introducing-agent-mcp.adoc
#, fuzzy
